Text: Re Enron Goldman Sachs Futures Documentation Cc Sheila Please let me know when we can do our conference call Looking forward to speaking with you and your colleagues shortly Please feel free to call with any questions Kind regards Mike wrote Michael Sorry I am a little to quick on the draw Ketan had Fed expressed Morgan Stanleys Futures Agreement to me and I had already forwarded to legal Thank you for the contact names Thanks Sheila
